# --- Data (do not commit datasets; keep only README) ---
# Only datasets in <project>/data/ - NOT the Python package src/.../data/ (re-included below).
**/data/*
!**/data/README.md
!**/src/**/*.py

# --- ML artifacts / tracking ---
mlruns/
mlartifacts/
mlflow.db
*.db
artifacts/

